The paper discusses the second shared task on multimodal machine translation and multilingual image description, which involves natural language processing (NLP) and computer vision (CV) techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), which covers NLP and related areas. The second likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), which covers CV and related areas. The third likely category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), which covers various AI techniques, including NLP and CV. The fourth likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), which covers various machine learning techniques, including those used in NLP and CV. The fifth likely category is cs.MM (Multimedia), which covers various multimedia-related topics, including multimodal machine translation and multilingual image description.
